OCCT viewer with draggable presentation. The presentation implements processing of the drag action.
To drag the presentation, just move the mouse over the presentation, press the mouse left button and move the mouse. 

The sample contains two shape presentations (cylinders).
One of presentation is draggable.

It displays the default trihedron of V3d view in the bottom left corner.
This sample is an extension of extras_viewerNative sample with the possibility to drag object.

Platform:
  Windows, x64, VStudio 2019, cmake 3.5.4
3rd-parties:
  occt:     7.6.0
  tbb:      2020.1
  freetype: 2.5.5
  qt:       5.15.1